RCE Rises Most in 6 Months as Fair Value Raised at RHB

-- B y   B a r r y   P o r t e r
-- 
2011-06-10T01:14:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/rce-rises-most-in-6-months-as-fair-value-raised-at-rhb-correct-.html
(Corrects fair value in first paragraph.)  RCE Capital Bhd. (RCE) , a Malaysian
consumer credit provider, rose the most in more than six months
in Kuala Lumpur trading after RHB Research Institute Sdn. raised
its fair value for the stock to 75 sen.  Its shares climbed 6 percent to 53 sen at 9:05 a.m. local
time, set for their biggest increase since Nov. 22.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Barry Porter at 
 bporter10@bloomberg.net  